The College of Letters & Science Presents...

SAVE YOUR SEMESTER WORKSHOPS!

Wed. March 13 | 12-1 pm

Thurs. March 14 | 12-1 pm

370 Dwinelle Hall

Worried about your grades? Get help navigating the options and resources available to you! This workshop covers L&S policies on grading option changes (P/NP), late change petitions, incomplete grades, and withdrawal. We'll also cover campus resources.
